main event: An unidentified object was sighted in the sky southeast of Newfoundland, observed for 10-15 minutes, and appeared to be stationary at approximately 600 yards high.
interesting points: The object was observed for 10-15 minutes, suggesting it was not a brief or fleeting sighting.
